Six Senses Residences, situated on the illustrious Palm Jumeirah Island in Dubai, represents a groundbreaking addition to the ultra-luxury hospitality chain, Six Senses Hotels Resorts Spas. This project, set for completion in Q4 2024, marks the brand's first foray into the United Arab Emirates, offering a distinctive blend of opulent accommodations and a strong commitment to wellness and sustainability.
Project Development
The development of Six Senses Residences is a collaboration between Six Senses Hotels Resorts Spas, Select Group, and Emirates Strategic Investments Company (ESIC). It encompasses a 60-key luxury hotel and 162 exceptional residences, making it a significant milestone in the realm of high-end hospitality on Palm Jumeirah Island.
Residence Types
Prospective buyers have a diverse range of residence types to choose from, including:

4-bedroom Royal Penthouses with optional private swimming pools.
3 and 4-bedroom Duplex Sky Villas offering panoramic views.
Imperial Penthouses exuding grandeur.
5-bedroom Beach Villas that epitomize luxury coastal living.

Residences span from 2,000 sq. ft to an expansive 14,600 sq. ft, offering a wide array of options to cater to the discerning tastes of buyers.
Sustainable Design and Amenities
The architectural concept of Six Senses Residences is inspired by coral, featuring undulating silhouettes, rooflines, and cellular facades. This design not only provides a unique and distinguished look but also ensures an environment protected from the harsh sun. The development seamlessly combines sustainability and wellness, boasting meticulously landscaped areas, dedicated running tracks, tennis and padel courts, and even a micro farm.
The centerpiece of the property is the luscious Zen garden, complete with mini jebels, courtyards, and valley paths. Residents can engage in a range of activities, including badminton, football, and yoga for their well-being. Natural ponds, Wadi boulders, and palm groves add to the resort-like ambiance. The property also features swimming pools and sundecks surrounded by native vegetation.
Pricing
The starting price for a 2-bedroom penthouse, spanning 2,000 sq. ft, is AED 9.4 million (USD 2.55 million). For those seeking the pinnacle of luxury, opulent 6,000 sq. ft villas are available for a minimum of AED 27 million (USD 7.35 million).
Location and Connectivity
Six Senses Residences enjoys a prime location on Palm Jumeirah's West Crescent, neighboring other renowned luxury hotels. Residents benefit from easy access to prominent F&B venues in Dubai. Additionally, the development is conveniently situated near essential facilities and leisure destinations, including Nakheel Mall, AlIttihad Park, The Palm Tower, and Golden Mile Galleria.
The Palm Jumeirah boasts its own monorail system, providing direct access to the mainland of Dubai via the Sheikh Zayed Road and the Beach Road. Two monorail stations, Atlantis The Palm and Atlantis Aquaventure, are located nearby, and Dubai International Airport is just a 35-minute drive away.
Six Senses Residences sets a new standard for luxury living and hospitality in Dubai, offering an unparalleled blend of opulent residences, wellness, and sustainability in a prime location on Palm Jumeirah Island.

Every detail has been carefully curated to elevate the living experience, setting a new standard for modern living.
Panoramic Views
Residents of Q Gardens Lofts are treated to breathtaking views of the iconic Dubai city skyline and the lush green surroundings. The project's elevated position allows for a panoramic vista that captivates the senses.
Amenities and Facilities
Q Gardens Lofts goes beyond the ordinary, offering an extensive array of amenities and facilities that cater to the diverse needs and desires of its residents. The Highbury is an upscale residential project by Ellington Properties, set in the dynamic and rapidly developing Mohammed Bin Rashid City in Dubai. This family-oriented project offers an exquisite lifestyle with a range of amenities and easy access to key locations in the emirate.
Contemporary Towers and Residential Units
The Highbury comprises two contemporary 29-story towers with a garden-strewn podium. This project caters to diverse living preferences, offering a variety of residential units, including studios, 1-2 bedroom apartments, 2-3 bedroom apartments with a maid's room, 4-bedroom penthouses, and duplex units.
Abundant Amenities
Residents of The Highbury will enjoy a wealth of amenities, ensuring a well-rounded and enjoyable living experience. These amenities include swimming pools, a children's splash pad, a BBQ area, a juice bar, and extensive sports facilities, featuring a state-of-the-art gymnasium, basketball court, paddle tennis court, yoga studio, and a running track. There are also communal spaces like a community lawn, a lounge, a clubhouse, cinema theatre, spa, and a dedicated children's playground.
Convenient Location and Access
This residential project is scheduled to be completed in Q4 2025. One of the key advantages of living at The Highbury is its strategic location, offering quick and easy connections to essential areas of Dubai. Downtown Dubai and Business Bay are just 15 minutes away, while Dubai Marina can be reached within 35 minutes.
Mohammed Bin Rashid City (MBR City)
The Highbury is situated within Mohammed Bin Rashid City, one of Dubai's significant multifunctional developments. MBR City is known for its ambitious plans, including The Mall of the World and a host of other amenities, such as hospitals, schools, hotels, and green spaces. MBR City actively encourages business and innovation and offers a range of property options, making it a sought-after investment destination.
Diverse Developer Presence
Mohammed Bin Rashid City hosts a diverse range of developers, including prominent names like Emaar and Meraas Holding, who work on large-scale residential and commercial projects such as Dubai Hills Estate. Other developers, like Sobha and Azizi, cater to a wide spectrum of housing needs, from high-end villas to budget-friendly apartments. The region boasts an average return on investment (ROI) of at least 8% and often provides discounts and bonuses for property purchases.
Flexible Payment Options
Buyers in The Highbury and other off-plan projects within MBR City can benefit from flexible payment plans and bank financing options. These options make purchasing real estate more accessible and convenient for both completed and under-construction projects, in line with stipulated parameters.
The Highbury offers an exceptional blend of luxury living, convenient location, and access to a wealth of amenities within the vibrant surroundings of Mohammed Bin Rashid City.

Elegance Amidst Nature
ORLA Infinity is designed to cater to open-minded individuals seeking a resort-style living experience that seamlessly integrates with the surrounding natural beauty. Clarity and Rejuvenation
ORLA Infinity aims to provide its residents with a sense of clarity and rejuvenation. The development has been meticulously planned to create an oasis of tranquility, allowing residents to escape the hustle and bustle of city life and find solace in a natural yet opulent setting.
Exclusive and Personalized Residences
Thoughtfully Positioned Design
Each of the 20 duplex residences within ORLA Infinity has been thoughtfully positioned to maximize the breathtaking views and provide a unique sense of space and privacy. The careful planning ensures that residents can savor the beauty of the surroundings from the comfort of their homes.
Seamless Integration of Spaces
The design of ORLA Infinity is centered around the concept of blending indoor and outdoor spaces effortlessly. This integration allows residents to enjoy the serene surroundings, the state-of-the-art facilities, and the dynamic cityscape beyond, all from the comfort of their residences.
Why Choose Orla Infinity
ORLA Infinity is not just a residential project; it's a masterpiece that offers a lifestyle like no other. The Jewel twin towers rise to an imposing twenty storeys, housing some of the worlds finest apartments Towering over a strategic location on the Dubai Marina and walking distance to the walk at JBR.

Vida Boulevard is a new project by Emaar at Downtown Dubai that combines stylish, world-class design with contemporary finishes and fittings. Residents have access to modern amenities including a swimming pool, fitness centre, and a dedicated area for children, set within the three-storey podium.

Discover VELA VIENTO, an extraordinary residential project located in the coveted Marasi Bay, part of the bustling Business Bay district. Managed by the esteemed Dorchester Collection, this project is designed to redefine luxury living, offering residents a lifestyle of unparalleled opulence and convenience.
Architectural Excellence
With meticulous attention to detail and design, VELA VIENTO is a testament to architectural excellence. Crafted in collaboration with OMNIYAT, Foster + Partners, and Gilles & Boissier, it promises to become one of the most prestigious developments in the region.
Diverse Residential Units
Choose from a range of residential options, including 24 bedroom apartments and a limited collection of 4-bedroom penthouses. The residences offer ample living space, ranging from 2,852 sq. ft to 14,413 sq. ft, with some units featuring private swimming pools.
Breathtaking Views

For families, several renowned educational institutions, including Blossom Downtown Nursery, Jumeirah International Nursery, and Dubai International School, are conveniently located within a 510 minute drive.

Investing in VELA VIENTO is an investment in your future. With stunning waterfront and skyline views, a host of premium amenities, and the backing of the Dorchester Collection, it offers an exceptional living experience. Furthermore, the potential for a 10% profit upon resale after project completion makes it a savvy investment choice. VELA VIENTO redefines luxury living in the vibrant Business Bay district.

One River Point is an extraordinary residential project by Ellington Properties, situated in the heart of Business Bay, Dubai, right on the picturesque waterfront of the Dubai Water Canal. This visionary development promises a luxurious and contemporary lifestyle, offering a range of residential options to suit various preferences and needs.

Panoramic windows fill the rooms with natural light, making your home feel both cozy and spacious while offering breathtaking views of the Dubai Water Canal.

Residents of One River Point will experience world-class amenities that enhance their quality of life. From an infinity pool, poolside lounge chairs, and gazebos to a BBQ area, fitness and yoga studios, and a terrace, every aspect of leisure and relaxation has been carefully considered. The complex also features a co-working space with a coffee shop and an exclusive immersion room for those seeking tranquility.
Luxury at Your Doorstep
Upon arrival, a concierge service awaits you in the resident and guest drop-off zone, leading to a bright and spacious lobby furnished with luxurious sofas. This is just the beginning of the premium lifestyle you can expect at One River Point.

Mercedes-Benz Places is a collaborative venture between Binghatti Developers and luxury automotive giant Mercedes-Benz, located in the heart of Downtown Dubai. This iconic residential project features 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments as well as penthouses, soaring to an impressive height of 341 meters across 65 floors, redefining opulence in the city's skyline.
Strategically positioned, the development offers unobstructed views of the renowned Burj Khalifa, surrounded by iconic structures such as the Dubai Mall and the Museum of the Future. The partnership between the developer and Mercedes-Benz is dedicated to a customer-centric approach, prioritizing the needs and desires of future residents.
Architectural excellence is a key highlight, boasting floor-to-ceiling heights of 4.2 meters that provide a sense of spaciousness and luxury. Each unit is adorned with a private pool, offering residents an exclusive retreat within their homes. The panoramic views from every unit facing the Burj Khalifa create an awe-inspiring living environment, incorporating the automotive giant's design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity' to create timeless and beautiful spaces.
The project, a result of meticulous planning and design, incorporates smart home technologies and intelligent mobility solutions, aiming to redefine comfort and convenience in modern living spaces. It envisions a lifestyle that seamlessly combines sophistication with the exclusivity of an oasis.
Key highlights include a premium collection of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments and penthouses, an astounding elevation of 341 meters across 65 floors, strategic location in Downtown Dubai, private pools in each residence, and adherence to the Mercedes-Benz design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity.'
In summary, Mercedes-Benz Places is an exclusive residential complex embodying ultra-luxury services, a collaboration between renowned developers and the iconic Mercedes-Benz brand, offering a harmonious oasis of serenity, aesthetic appeal, and a lifestyle that seamlessly blends automotive excellence with architectural grandeur.

Set on the shores of Emaar Beachfront, Address Residences The Bay is where luxury living meets the rhythm of the sea. Developed by Emaar in partnership with Address Hotels + Resorts, the project offers residents more than just a home  its a lifestyle defined by elegance, comfort, and resort-style exclusivity.
The tower features thoughtfully designed 13 bedroom apartments, penthouses, and limited townhouses, each with sweeping views of the Arabian Gulf, Dubai Marina, and Palm Jumeirah. Spacious layouts, premium finishes, and floor-to-ceiling windows create homes that are both sophisticated and light-filled.
What sets The Bay apart is its direct private beach access, a rare privilege in Dubai. Residents enjoy world-class amenities including infinity pools, landscaped decks, fitness facilities, childrens play areas, and a vibrant promenade lined with dining and retail. Every element is designed to mirror the luxury and service standards of the Address brand.
Perfectly positioned between Dubai Marina and Palm Jumeirah, the development offers effortless connectivity to the city while preserving the calm of waterfront living. With completion scheduled for Q4 2026, Address Residences The Bay is an opportunity to secure a branded beachfront home in one of Dubais most exclusive new communities.

Claydon House at Meydan, developed by Ellington Properties, represents a pinnacle of luxury living in Dubai's Mohammed Bin Rashid City. Offering premium designed 1, 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments, this high-rise building stands out for its architectural elegance and exceptional amenities.
Location-wise, it enjoys a prime spot within Meydan, with stunning views of the Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary and the Downtown Dubai skyline. Residents have direct access to a crystal-clear lagoon, enhancing the allure of the development.
The apartments are meticulously crafted to seamlessly integrate indoor and outdoor living spaces, allowing residents to immerse themselves in natural beauty. Inside, every corner exudes luxury and comfort. From a tranquil library to a cinema room, from fitness and boxing facilities to yoga studios, the amenities cater to diverse needs and preferences.
The development also features a ground-floor retail promenade and a community lagoon, redefining urban living. With its 38 residential floors atop 5 podium levels, it ensures exclusivity and privacy for residents. Ample parking and state-of-the-art elevators add to the practicality and luxury.
The first-floor amenities focus on leisure and recreation, with an infinity-edge leisure pool, sun lounger area, fitness studio, and children's play area, fostering a sense of community and wellness.
Key highlights include its diverse range of apartment options, impressive architectural design, prime location within Meydan, meticulously crafted interiors, and comprehensive amenities catering to residents' diverse lifestyles. Whether it's indulging in leisurely activities or enjoying the upscale facilities, Claydon House promises an extraordinary lifestyle experience in the heart of Dubai.

Unit Types:


2-3 Bedroom Apartments: These luxurious apartments offer spacious living areas infused with nature-inspired designs. Ranging from 2,002 sq. ft to 14,100 sq. ft, they provide ample space for comfortable living.


4 Bedroom Penthouses: Half-floor penthouses boasting panoramic views of Dubai Harbour, Bluewaters Island, and Palm Jumeirah. These premium residences offer lavish amenities and expansive living spaces.


5 Bedroom Triplexes: Sky Mansions designed with sophistication and luxury in mind, offering unparalleled comfort and style across three levels.


Amenities:


Wellness Facilities: Residents have access to state-of-the-art wellness amenities, including a large gym, spa center, swimming pool, and relaxation areas. The biophilic design promotes mental and physical well-being, complemented by Sleep With Six Senses bedroom amenities and a wellness closet equipped with fitness equipment and mood-enhancing sensory tools.


Innovative Wellness Zones: The building features four distinct zones, each occupying a separate floor: Connectivity, Balance, Longevity, and Horizon. These zones offer a range of amenities, from party rooms and cinemas to saunas, jacuzzis, health and fitness facilities, and breathtaking views from the 109th-floor lounge.


Community and Entertainment: To foster a sense of community, residents can enjoy lounge areas, community gathering spaces, a game room, and a cinema. The Skydeck on the 109th floor features an 82-ft lap pool, providing an extraordinary setting for socializing and relaxation.


Location and Accessibility:


Situated in Dubai Marina, residents enjoy easy access to iconic attractions, leisure options, and dining venues such as Marina Beach, Dubai Marina Mall, The Walk at JBR, and more.


The location offers convenient proximity to Downtown Dubai, Dubai Marina, and both DXB and DWC Airports, ensuring residents can easily access the city's key destinations.


Payment Plan and Handover:

The starting price for these residences is 5.8 million AED, with a flexible 40/60 payment plan.
The handover is scheduled for Q3 2028, providing ample time for interested buyers to plan their investment.

Overall, Six Senses Residences Dubai Marina offers a premium lifestyle characterized by luxury, wellness, and unparalleled amenities, setting a new standard for residential living in Dubai.

One Sankari Marasi Business Bay is set to redefine luxury living in one of Dubai's most dynamic districts. This flagship project by Sankari Properties offers an exclusive collection of ultra-luxury apartments, catering to the discerning tastes of investors and residents alike.
Location: Situated in the vibrant Business Bay, the development enjoys a prestigious location known for its modern infrastructure, bustling commercial districts, and proximity to iconic landmarks and business hubs. The area is well-connected, making it a coveted spot for both living and investment.
Property Features: The twin residential towers offer a range of three, four, and five-bedroom apartments, each designed to occupy entire floors, ensuring maximum privacy and security. Unit sizes start at approximately 600 m, providing spacious and luxurious living spaces.
Amenities: Residents will have access to world-class amenities, including fitness studios, sports centers, clinics, supermarkets, and restaurants. The development promises high-end finishes, durable construction, and next-level comfort. Facilities include fitness centers, swimming pools, yacht marina, kids' play areas, and more.
Design and Quality: One Sankari Marasi Business Bay showcases exceptional design and interiors by world-renowned architects and designers, focusing on quality, durability, and luxury.
Pricing: Luxury apartments in this development start at $10,000,000 (36,724,000 AED), presenting a significant investment opportunity in Dubai's real estate market. The location and ultra-luxury offerings make it an attractive option for high-net-worth individuals and investors.
Investment Potential: Business Bay is known for its strong demand and growth potential, making properties in One Sankari Marasi Business Bay a promising investment. The combination of prime location, exquisite design, and world-class amenities positions this development as a standout choice for those seeking luxury and exclusivity in Dubai.

Unrivaled Location and Unforgettable Experiences
Residents of Dubai Harbour Residences will enjoy unrivaled proximity to the beachfront, with sunrise walks on sandy shores and boundless adventures on the ocean waters right at their doorstep. Social gatherings enriched by gentle breezes and breathtaking views become the norm.
These homes boast award-winning marinas, a private beach, and direct access to Sheikh Zayed Road, opening a world of remarkable experiences both on land and at sea.
 
Award-winning Architecture and Inspired Design
